{"tid":1569192,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【左膠入嚟】當手足還擊時，記得大嗌「落雨」同埋「唔好打」","createTime":"2019-09-14T13:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T17:32:40.000Z","uid":23094,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9dcbf4a5036121ef3427cc012b71175cfeb7712e","tid":1569192,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"嗱我就唔鼓吹暴力嘅，對住冇良知物種除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而自衛還擊／保護他人嗰啲極其量只係叫做以武制暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗌「落雨」開遮可以保護手足<br />\n嗌「唔好打」同時可以滿足你左膠嘅心態<br />\n一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔出手冇人會怪你，大家都明白每個人都有自己嘅顧慮<br />\n但係唔好阻住手足做嘢，講好咗尊重前線任何決定㗎嘛<br />\n你可能冇能力保護被對家襲擊嗰位手足，但係你至少可以保護出手還擊嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n前線做嘢一定有用腦諗過，會唔會係鬼／會唔會重手得滯⋯⋯<br />\n所以唔需要擔心埋呢啲無謂嘢<br />\n但係如果你擔心嘅係打人會失民心咁唔該你收皮<br />\n因為手足出得手嘅話，永遠都係因為對家出手先<br />\n如果還手都驚失民心就唔該快啲完撚咗場革命，一齊等清算算數"},{"pid":"c3600e321ccb7fab7a102913dc698fbc61aa5739","tid":1569192,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"993de217baa34079d866e68cfcc185a5ea347f72","tid":1569192,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3600e321ccb7fab7a102913dc698fbc61aa5739","tid":1569192,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?